00:00:47.310 --> 00:00:51.680
BILL NYE: Yeah, that'd be great,
because I was really upbeat.

00:00:51.680 --> 00:00:53.164
Let's knock that down.

00:00:53.164 --> 00:00:54.580
VIKRAM BAJAJ: Click
