00:23:19.360 --> 00:23:23.090
and all these things on how
to defend your otherwise

00:23:23.090 --> 00:23:25.810
completely unreasonable
belief and so on.

00:23:25.810 --> 00:23:28.300
And that's what's
really troubling.

00:23:28.300 --> 00:23:29.240
VIKRAM BAJAJ: I agree.

