significant changes.

00:24:22.670 --> 00:24:26.180
These things happen
regularly, like a clock.

00:24:26.180 --> 00:24:30.230
So you can assess the speed
at which DNA is changing,

00:24:30.230 --> 00:24:33.140
and then you can work back to
when the Neanderthals and us

00:24:33.140 --> 00:24:38.520
