same game and interacting.

00:24:38.520 --> 00:24:41.380
Can we say "interacting" here?

00:24:41.380 --> 00:24:43.210
VIKRAM BAJAJ: Yes.

00:24:43.210 --> 00:24:44.931
In fact, you need not
use the euphemism.

00:24:44.931 --> 00:24:45.430
But--

00:24:45.430 --> 00:24:46.638
BILL NYE: They were doing it.

00:24:46.638 --> 00:24:48.400
