it double-sexual.

00:29:25.150 --> 00:29:30.580
They just start reproducing
without doing it.

00:29:30.580 --> 00:29:33.540
And then those
reproduced fish are

00:29:33.540 --> 00:29:35.792
more susceptible to parasites.

00:29:35.792 --> 00:29:37.500
But then, when it
rains again and there's

00:29:37.500 --> 00:29:39.980
