So the single most
important thing

00:55:05.630 --> 00:55:07.960
we can all do right
now, I believe,

00:55:07.960 --> 00:55:11.190
is talk about climate change.

00:55:11.190 --> 00:55:12.500
Just raise awareness.

00:55:12.500 --> 00:55:15.830
Just make it part of our
everyday conversation,

00:55:15.830 --> 00:55:19.640
because we are all living
in a little bit of denial

00:55:19.640 --> 00:55:20.540
of climate change.

00:55:20.540 --> 00:55:23.340
And I'm the first
to say, me too.

00:55:23.340 --> 00:55:24.040
I, as well.

00:55:24.040 --> 00:55:25.630
Mea culpa.

00:55:25.630 --> 00:55:27.600
By raising awareness
of climate change,

00:55:27.600 --> 00:55:29.150
we will get something done.

00:55:29.150 --> 00:55:32.880
Now, just by way
of example, my dad

00:55:32.880 --> 00:55:38.050
took a job in 1941
on Wake Island.

00:55:38.050 --> 00:55:39.790
I don't know if you've
ever heard of it.

00:55:39.790 --> 00:55:41.730
You go to Hawaii, and
then you go about that

00:55:41.730 --> 00:55:44.770
far again to Wake.

00:55:44.770 --> 00:55:46.730
It's still a tactically
important place.

00:55:46.730 --> 00:55:51.060
There are about 700 US Air Force
landings, airplane landings,

00:55:51.060 --> 00:55:51.980
every year.

00:55:51.980 --> 00:55:53.900
When you went to
Asia, in the old days,

00:55:53.900 --> 00:55:58.700
you'd fly from San Francisco
to Pearl Harbor to Wake

00:55:58.700 --> 00:56:02.170
and then on to Midway,
usually, in Shanghai, in China.

00:56:02.170 --> 00:56:05.400
But without Wake Island,
you couldn't make that trip.

00:56:05.400 --> 00:56:09.980
Anyway, everybody thought,
well, things are going to be OK.

00:56:09.980 --> 00:56:13.160
There's never going to
be a war in the Pacific.

00:56:13.160 --> 00:56:15.420
World War II is never
going to come to the US.

00:56:15.420 --> 00:56:17.380
Everything's going to be fine.

00:56:17.380 --> 00:56:20.260
And my dad took that job, and
then he ended up in prison camp

00:56:20.260 --> 00:56:21.130
for four years.

00:56:21.130 --> 00:56:23.410
And so I don't recommend
that, by the way.

00:56:23.410 --> 00:56:27.110
But people in the US, just
looking at it historically--

00:56:27.110 --> 00:56:30.000
and this new movie came out
about Turing, Alan Turing,

00:56:30.000 --> 00:56:34.560
and everything-- people
thought the problem is so big,

00:56:34.560 --> 00:56:36.380
it won't happen.

00:56:36.380 --> 00:56:40.690
And I think we're all doing that
with respect to climate change.

00:56:40.690 --> 00:56:41.800
So talk about it.

00:56:41.800 --> 00:56:43.000
Talk about climate change.

00:56:43.000 --> 00:56:44.100
Talk about evolution.

00:56:44.100 --> 00:56:47.680
Get in fights over the Isaac
Newton's birthday holiday

00:56:47.680 --> 00:56:50.075
Christmas table.

