Isaac Newton was born
on Christmas day,

00:56:51.700 --> 00:56:54.680
by the way, as
reckoned in Britain.

00:56:54.680 --> 00:56:56.710
In Italy, it was the
fourth of January.

00:56:56.710 --> 00:56:58.900
They were still not
agreeing on the calendar.

00:56:58.900 --> 00:57:01.240
But I always say,
Isaac Newton's mom

00:57:01.240 --> 00:57:03.790
thought it was Christmas
day, for crying out loud.

00:57:03.790 --> 00:57:07.670
So you guys, just talk
about climate change.

00:57:07.670 --> 00:57:09.600
And then, together,
I strongly believe,

00:57:09.600 --> 00:57:11.780
as I look at history and
the greatest generation

00:57:11.780 --> 00:57:14.670
and what have you,
we can do this.

00:57:14.670 --> 00:57:16.360
We can change the world.

